OL,5, King Charles has asked for a surge in  
OL,6, profits from a #1bn per year Crown     
OL,7, Estate offshore wind farm deal to be   
OL,8, used for the "wider public good",      
OL,9, rather than for the Royal Family.      
OL,11,FThe Sovereign Grant, which pays the    
OL,12,Frunning costs of the Royal Household,  
OL,13,Fis currently based on 25% of Crown     
OL,14,FEstate profits.                        
OL,16,FThose profits will see a big increase  
OL,17,Fwith payments from six new wind farms. 
OL,19,FKing Charles is proposing to reduce the
OL,20,Froyal slice of these higher earnings.  
